title: Beya Bouabdallah
text: Beya Bouabdallah (born December 24, 1944) is a former <a href="Tunisia">Tunisia</a>n female <a href="basketball">basketball</a> player, female <a href="handball">handball</a> player, female <a href="volleyball">volleyball</a> player and female <a href="athletics%20%28sport%29">athletics</a> player.
